A free and open source spoiler blocker.
Type any phrase to block it from websites you browse.
You aren't limited by current shows or presets.
Spoiled was designed to make adding and removing
phrases as fast and easy as possible.
Spoiled covers up all text and images containing terms you provide.
I created Spoiled because I didn't trust that other
blockers were handling my data with care. Many even ask
for social network feed access. I thought making a quick little
spoiler blocker would be fairly easy and that maybe others
would use it too. All the code is open source and we use no
analytics of any kind, so we have no access to the terms you
enter or the sites you browse.
